ation folds as instructed.\n","\n"],"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"PJPcZlmuMx_L"}},{"source":["from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split, KFold\n","\n","# Split data into training and testing sets\n","X_train_all, X_test_all, y_train_all, y_test_all = train_test_split(\n","    X_all, y, test_size=0.2, random_state=42\n",")\n","X_train_2, X_test_2, y_train_2, y_test_2 = train_test_split(\n","    X_2, y, test_size=0.2, random_state=42\n",")\n","\n","# Create cross-validation folds\n","kf_all = KFold(n_splits=5, random_state=42, shuffle=True)\n","kf_2 = KFold(n_splits=5, random_state=42, shuffle=True)"],"cell_type":"code","metadata":{"id":"gwxmHRw8MyO5","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1743417987533,"user_tz":-480,"elapsed":20,"user":{"displayName":"Cheung Kiu Lung","userId":"01351186673283109246"}}},"execution_count":66,"outputs":[]},{"source":["## Model training\n","\n","### Subtask:\n","Train Logistic Regression, Decision Tree, and Random Forest models using 5-fold cross-validation on both the full feature set and the two-feature subset.\n"],"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"a_giYfAtM3qS"}},{"source":["**Reasoning**:\n","Import necessary libraries and initialize the models. Then perform cross-validation and training for all features and two features.\n","\n"],"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"L6EBeK3WM4e_"}},{"source":["from sklearn.linear_model import LogisticRegression\n","from sklearn.tree import DecisionTreeClassifier\n","from sklearn.ensemble import RandomForestClassifier\n","from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score\n","import numpy as np\n","\n","# Initialize models\n","logreg = LogisticRegression()\n","dtree = DecisionTreeClassifier()\n","rf = RandomForestClassifier(n_estimators=100)\n","\n","# Store cross-validation accuracy results\n","accuracy_all_features = {'Logistic Regression': [], 'Decision Tree': [], 'Random Forest': []}\n","accuracy_two_features = {'Logistic Regression': [], 'Decision Tree': [], 'Random Forest': []}\n","\n","# Cross-validation and training (All Features)\n","for train_index, test_index in kf_all.split(X_train_all):\n","    X_train, X_test = X_train_all.iloc[train_index], X_train_all.iloc[test_index]\n","    y_train, y_test = y_train_all.iloc[train_index], y_train_all.iloc[test_index]\n","\n","    logreg.fit(X_train, y_train)\n","    dtree.fit(X_train, y_train)\n","    rf.fit(X_train, y_train)\n","\n","    accuracy_all_features['Logistic Regression'].append(accuracy_score(y_test, logreg.predict(X_test)))\n","    accuracy_all_features['Decision Tree'].append(accuracy_score(y_test, dtree.predict(X_test)))\n","    accuracy_all_features['Random Forest'].append(accuracy_score(y_test, rf.predict(X_test)))\n","\n","# Cross-validation and training (Two Features)\n","for train_index, test_index in kf_2.split(X_train_2):\n","    X_train, X_test = X_train_2.iloc[train_index], X_train_2.iloc[test_index]\n","    y_train, y_test = y_train_2.iloc[train_index], y_train_2.iloc[test_index]\n","\n","    logreg.fit(X_train, y_train)\n","    dtree.fit(X_train, y_train)\n","    rf.fit(X_train, y_train)\n","\n","    accuracy_two_features['Logistic Regression'].append(accuracy_score(y_test, logreg.predict(X_test)))\n","    accuracy_two_features['Decision Tree'].append(accuracy_score(y_test, dtree.predict(X_test)))\n","    accuracy_two_features['Random Forest'].append(accuracy_score(y_test, rf.predict(X_test)))\n","\n","print(\"Accuracy with all features:\", accuracy_all_features)\n","print(\"Accuracy with two features:\", accuracy_two_features)"],"cell_type":"code","metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"QghXmiKBM4uy","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1743417991596,"user_tz":-480,"elapsed":4061,"user":{"displayName":"Cheung Kiu Lung","userId":"01351186673283109246"}},"outputId":"5a448857-455a-40f5-b156-fd5de470b2ab"},"execution_count":67,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["Accuracy with all features: {'Logistic Reg